data.description: Located in a scenic area bordered by a creek and forrest, Ridge Creek is situated on approximately 45 acres of rolling hills. Conveniently located just two miles from I-74 and Rt. 150, Ridge Creek has quick access to shopping, entertainment, and the businesses Champaign-Urbana offers. Walking paths connecting to Lake of The Woods allow for an active lifestyle. The lake will be expanded to 3 acres and will be accessible by the walking path.
